Suggested Enhancements for your Gem
To make this data more meaningful, I recommend adding these three "Enhanced Metrics" to your monthly report:
1. Outreach Efficiency Ratio
Instead of just looking at the number of emails, calculate how many emails it takes to get a candidate to "Advance."
$$\text{Efficiency} = \frac{\text{Emails Sent}}{\text{Candidates Advanced}}$$
Why: A lower number means the recruiter is writing highly effective, targeted emails rather than "spamming."
2. The "Active Sourcing" vs. "Process Management" Split
You can have the Gem categorize the recruiters based on their behavior:
Sourcing Profile: High "Candidates Added" but lower "Interviews Scheduled" (Top of Funnel).
Closing Profile: Low "Candidates Added" but high "Scorecards/Interviews" (End of Funnel).
Why: This helps you see if your team is balanced or if everyone is stuck in "Interview Mode" and neglecting the top of the funnel.
3. Platform ROI (Activity per Log-in)
$$\text{Daily Impact} = \frac{\text{Activity Score}}{\text{Days Logged In}}$$
Why: This identifies "Power Users." For example, if someone only logged in 10 times but had the same activity as someone who logged in 25 times, they are using the platform much more efficiently.
